article.description: — Colby Rogers had 18 points as Siena topped Army 83-67 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Rogers scores 18 to carry Siena past Army 83-67
article.linkText: Rogers scores 18 to carry Siena past Army 83-67
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — Colby Rogers had 18 points as Siena topped Army 83-67 on Tuesday night. Anthony Gaines pitched in with 16 points and seven rebounds for the Saints (2-5). Nick Hopkins added 11 points, while Aidan Carpenter scored 10. Josh Caldwell had 19 points and seven rebounds for the Black Knights (4-3). Jalen Rucker added 16 points. Charlie Peterson had 10 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Portions of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
